				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you are using an assembler that assumes 8 KB banks, then $C000 must be assigned to the <em>second to last</em> bank in the cart, and $E000 must be assigned to the <em>last</em> bank. For a 32 KB S*ROM, $C000 should be bank 2 and $E000 should be bank 3.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

